+ * init_idle - set up an idle thread for a given CPU
+ * @idle: task in question
+ * @cpu: CPU the idle task belongs to
+ *
+ * NOTE: this function does not set the idle thread's NEED_RESCHED
+ * flag, to make booting more robust.
